data.description: Handsome and stately, Lennar's 2-story, 3,423 square feet, Prescott floor plan projects a sophistication that catches the eye of those looking for perfection. Inside, this 2-story home is best described as grand.  Enter through the front porch with the formal dining room set off the foyer into an open family room, nook and kitchen. The impressive kitchen boasts a gourmet island, rich cabinetry, GE appliances, and plenty of counter space. Besides a good-sized walk-in pantry for storage, there's also an optional butler's pantry conveniently situated adjacent to the formal dining area. The study and powder room are set off the separate single car garage.  The fourth bedroom is ideal for guests, college student or live-in parent with its full bath and easy access the separate 2-car garage that has an owner's entry into the house as well. Upstairs you will find the master suite split from two secondary bedrooms. The master suite is spacious and includes a luxurious master bathroom great for indulging yourself with a long soak in the oversized garden tub displayed between the his and her vanities. Or, take a relaxing shower that is separate from the tub.  This suite also includes a huge walk-in closet and private lavatory.  The loft is large, open and next to the craft and laundry room.
